  "description": "Semiconductor-specific chemical safety, toxicology, ventilation engineering, PPE systems, emergency response, and waste management for hazardous process chemicals (HF, silane, arsine, phosphine). Distinct from general occupational health by focus on ultra-hazardous hydride gases, pyrophoric materials, and semiconductor waste streams. Organized by functional safety domain: chemical hazards, ventilation, PPE, emergency response, waste treatment.",
